73
00:08:10,026 --> 00:08:13,696
Once again, I salute my Imperator...

74
00:08:13,947 --> 00:08:15,573
Furiosa!

75
00:08:15,823 --> 00:08:16,823
And I salute...

76
00:08:16,991 --> 00:08:19,619
