90
00:10:23,284 --> 00:10:24,744
Clear off!

91
00:10:26,412 --> 00:10:28,331
Get them all off!

92
00:10:28,873 --> 00:10:29,874
Clear off!

93
00:10:30,124 --> 00:10:31,918
Get them all off.

94
00:10:32,835 --> 00:10:35,004
