257
00:29:18,793 --> 00:29:19,377
Witness me...

258
00:29:19,628 --> 00:29:20,628
Blood Bag!

259
00:29:24,674 --> 00:29:26,092
Witness!

260
00:29:50,075 --> 00:29:52,244
I live, I die, I live again!

261
00:29:58,833 --> 00:29:59,834
Aah!

262
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:36,718
